    <body.content>
      <block class="lead_paragraph">
        <p>Michael Patti, vice chairman and worldwide creative director at Y&amp;R Advertising, New York, part of the Young &amp; Rubicam Brands unit of the WPP Group, left to pursue other interests, the agency said. His departure came four months after the arrival of a new chief executive at Y&amp;R, Hamish McLennan, who has described plans to ''invest in our talent'' as he remakes the agency.</p>
      </block>
